config.script:
# Open the condenser fan controls side panel.
	
	system.perspective.openDock('controlSidePanel',params={'controlViewPath':'Building Automation Demo/Page/Controls/Framework/AHU 2/Sm/Control Panels/Condenser Fan Controls','compNumb':''})

# Open the condenser pump controls side panel.
	
	system.perspective.openDock('controlSidePanel',params={'controlViewPath':'Building Automation Demo/Page/Controls/Framework/AHU 2/Sm/Control Panels/Condenser Pump Controls','compNumb':''})

# Open the main compressor controls side panel.
	
	system.perspective.openDock('controlSidePanel',params={'controlViewPath':'Building Automation Demo/Page/Controls/Framework/AHU 2/Sm/Control Panels/Main Compressor Controls','compNumb':''})
